request.description:
Get a list of claims that match the information provided in the parameters. If multiple claims are found, they will be returned as an array, sorted by the `created_date`, ascending. 

You can also view claims in an HTML report format by clicking the 'Visualize' tab in the response pane. This shows a condensed version of the claims for easy reading. The code for the visualization is found in the 'Tests' tab if you'd like to fork and modify it to suit your needs. 

![Claims table](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20145532/128721309-9e0a1f7e-bc11-469b-b073-ab86d9897e77.png)
